# multiple-discriminated-unions-test

Test fixture with multiple discriminated unions to verify Kind types
are properly namespaced and don't conflict.
This reproduces the original bug where both unions would generate
the same Kind.ts file causing conflicts.


**Version:** 1.0.0

## Installation

```bash
go get example.com/sdk
```

## Usage

```go
package main

import (
    "context"
    "example.com/sdk"
)

func main() {
    sdk := multiple-discriminated-unions-test.New("https://api.example.com")
    // Use the SDK...
}
```
